data.title: G McNeilus Wind Farm Dodge Center
data.meta_description: Power plant details for G McNeilus Wind Farm Dodge Center, a wind farm located in Dodge Center, MN. View the monthly generation and consumption, generator details, and more for G McNeilus Wind Farm Dodge Center
data.text:
G McNeilus Wind Farm Dodge Center is ranked #34 out of 123 wind farms in Minnesota in terms of total annual net electricity generation.

G McNeilus Wind Farm Dodge Center generated 38.3 GWh during the 3-month period between September 2022 to December 2022.
